text: Tokkel Samuud deqsita marah digaalah Namri yemeete waqdi, Nabii Saalic kee kâ luk yeemene mara finqak naggosneh Nek yan Racmatah, woo ayróh (usun edde fingiten ayró kinnuk) xixxibaanee kee mangacannak ken naggosneh, diggah Nabii Mucammadow Jcsakeiķge ku Rabbi usuk Qandeliiy, atka kaak gibdiih isi Reedal kulliimik maysó li kinni
